Hey Paul - We’re one of the 3rd party integrations - <https://www.invoicestack.co|Invoice Stack>. Set up is simple as we use HubSpot’s native quotes and integrate directly with QuickBooks, and we offer free onboarding on our Pro plans and above.
There’s a free trial and you’re also welcome to book a demo and chat through your use case and see if it’s a good fit. Or feel free to DM me any questions on here.
